autocmd FileType go nmap <buffer> <nowait> <Leader>r     <Plug>(go-run)
autocmd FileType go nmap <buffer> <nowait> <Leader>b     <Plug>(go-build)
autocmd FileType go nmap <buffer> <nowait> <Leader>t     <Plug>(go-test)
